{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778726842672,"sessionID":"ses_1dba1735effe7w9m8bQXcNkDCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260513-003-r3s2\ntitle: 4-entry Return Address Stack for JALR returns\ncategory: predictor\nmotivation: |\n  The current static predictor correctly predicts JAL and backward branches,\n  but every function return (JALR reading x1, writing x0) is predicted\n  not-taken, incurring a 2-cycle pipeline flush. CoreMark contains frequent\n  function calls and returns. A small Return Address Stack predicts return\n  addresses with very high accuracy for minimal area cost, directly\n  improving IPC without touching the critical EX or MEM paths.\nhypothesis: |\n  Add a 4-entry Return Address Stack (RAS). In the IF stage, detect\n  return-pattern JALR instructions (opcode=JALR, rd=x0, rs1=x1); when the\n  RAS is non-empty, predict taken and steer next_pc to the RAS top entry.\n  In the ID stage, detect calls (JAL or JALR writing x1) and push PC+4\n  onto the RAS; detect returns and pop the RAS. RAS updates are gated by\n  !flush so wrong-path instructions never corrupt the stack. EX-stage\n  redirect logic continues to verify predictions and correct mispredicts.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 5\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/ras.sv\n    description: New 4-entry Return Address Stack module with push/pop/top/empty ports.\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: Detect return-pattern JALR; when RAS is non-empty assert predict_taken and use ras_top as predict_target.\n  - file: rtl/id_stage.sv\n    description: Detect calls (JAL/JALR writing x1) to push PC+4; detect returns to pop RAS; gate both on !flush.\n  - file: rtl/core.sv\n    description: Instantiate RAS and wire top/empty to IF stage, push/pop/addr to ID stage.\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep2/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-003-r3s2.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep2/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-003-r3s2.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-003-r3s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778726842665,"end":1778726842671}},"id":"prt_e24618be0001uJI5WysZaamFpy","sessionID":"ses_1dba1735effe7w9m8bQXcNkDCR","messageID":"msg_e24614cc80011MI7FWIhT28N2z"}}
