{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778738452688,"sessionID":"ses_1daf827b0ffeG2lLOscjGc1iiX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"write:1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-001-r8s0\ntitle: Precompute PC+4 in ID stage and pipeline to EX to eliminate redundant adders\ncategory: micro_opt\nmotivation: |\n  The EX stage recomputes pc+4 in three separate places: JAL/JALR return-address\n  (alu_result), misaligned-trap fallback (pc_next), and not-taken mispredict\n  redirect_target. Each recomputation is a 32-bit adder on paths that are known\n  to be timing-sensitive (redirect goes from EX back to IF). By computing pc+4\n  once in the ID stage and carrying it through the id_ex_t pipeline register,\n  EX replaces those adders with a register read, shortening the mispredict\n  recovery path and the EX/MEM write-data setup path without affecting IPC.\nhypothesis: |\n  Add a pc_plus4 field to id_ex_t (core_pkg.sv). In id_stage.sv latch\n  reg_q.pc_plus4 <= in.pc + 32'd4 alongside the existing ID/EX state. In\n  ex_stage.sv replace every occurrence of in.pc + 32'd4 with in.pc_plus4:\n  (1) alu_result for JAL/JALR, (2) pc_next on misalign trap, (3) redirect_target\n  when the branch/jump is not taken. This removes three 32-bit adders from the\n  EX stage at the cost of one adder in ID and 32 extra flip-flops in the ID/EX\n  register. Because the ID/EX capture path is not the current critical path,\n  the net effect should be a small Fmax improvement (2-4 MHz) with zero IPC\n  change.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 2\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/core_pkg.sv\n    description: Add logic [31:0] pc_plus4 to the id_ex_t struct.\n  - file: rtl/id_stage.sv\n    description: Latch reg_q.pc_plus4 <= in.pc + 32'd4 in the ID/EX register.\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: Replace in.pc + 32'd4 with in.pc_plus4 in the JAL/JALR alu_result mux, the misalign pc_next mux, and the redirect_target assignment.\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep2/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r8s0.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep2/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r8s0.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-001-r8s0.yaml","time":{"start":1778738452669,"end":1778738452687}},"id":"prt_e2512989b001Lat6a1ojPpmtdL","sessionID":"ses_1daf827b0ffeG2lLOscjGc1iiX","messageID":"msg_e250b53c5002umKN3ZRY9fhGvh"}}
