ange). Update the BTB in the MEM stage from the\\nEX/MEM register using the resolved JALR target (pc_next) and the JALR's own PC, gated\\non valid && is_jalr && !is_illegal. This eliminates mispredicts on repeated indirect\\ncalls and jump-table branches without affecting the existing correct prediction paths.\\n\", \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 3, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/btb.sv\", \"description\": \"New 4-entry direct-mapped BTB module. Read port indexed by PC[3:2]\\n      returning hit and target. Update port writes valid+tag+target on resolved JALR.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/if_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add btb_hit and btb_target inputs. Extend predict_taken / predict_target\\n      to select BTB target for non-return JALR on hit, preserving existing JAL / branch\\n    / RAS return prediction paths.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/core.sv\", \"description\": \"Instantiate BTB at top level. Wire read side to IF stage (using io_imemAddr\\n      as read PC). Wire update side from EX/MEM register (pc, pc_next, ctrl.is_jalr,\\n      ctrl.is_illegal, valid).\"}]}, \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 3, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/btb.sv\", \"description\": \"New 4-entry direct-mapped BTB module. Read port indexed by PC[3:2]\\n      returning hit and target. Update port writes valid+tag+target on resolved JALR.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/if_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add btb_hit and btb_target inputs. Extend predict_taken / predict_target\\n      to select BTB target for non-return JALR on hit, preserving existing JAL / branch\\n    / RAS return prediction paths.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/core.sv\", \"description\": \"Instantiate BTB at top level. Wire read side to IF stage (using io_imemAddr\\n      as read PC). Wire update side from EX/MEM register (pc, pc_next, ctrl.is_jalr,\\n      ctrl.is_illegal, valid).\"}], \"outcome\": \"regression\", \"fitness\": 291.79, \"delta_pct\": -11.9, \"vs_baseline\": 3.17, \"fmax_mhz\": 123.89, \"ipc_coremark\": 2e-06, \"cycles\": 4245805, \"iterations\": 10, \"lut4\": 10677, \"ff\": 2278, \"seeds\": [139.98, 122.38, 123.89], \"formal_passed\": true, \"cosim_passed\": true, \"error\": null, \"implementation_notes\": \"\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-14T09:35:25.731940Z\", \"slot\": 2, \"round_id\": 14, \"scribe_skipped\": \"TimeoutError: scribe timed out after 240s\"}\n","exit":0,"description":"Check latest log entries","truncated":false},"title":"Check latest log entries","time":{"start":1778751741917,"end":1778751741919}},"id":"prt_e25dd9cd50011tQfwGfdjBJJEB","sessionID":"ses_1da23e9c5ffeelLZA5icmOJ2op","messageID":"msg_e25dd4ae70016zwcoWLeQK7Az4"}}
