arget address as PC+imm.  When a\\ntaken prediction is made, the IF stage overrides next_pc with the\\ntarget instead of PC+4.  The EX stage recomputes the same prediction\\nfrom the instruction in EX; it asserts redirect only on mispredict\\n(predicted taken but not taken, or vice versa).  This removes the\\nflush penalty for correctly predicted branches and jumps without\\nrequiring any extra pipeline registers or state RAM, keeping LUT usage\\nwithin the remaining budget.\\n\", \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 8, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/if_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add combinational BTFN+JAL predictor that computes target from imem_data and overrides next_pc when a taken prediction is made.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/ex_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Recompute the static prediction in EX and assert redirect only when the actual branch/jump outcome differs from the prediction.\"}]}, \"expected_impact\": {\"fitness_delta_pct\": 8, \"confidence\": \"medium\"}, \"changes\": [{\"file\": \"rtl/if_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Add combinational BTFN+JAL predictor that computes target from imem_data and overrides next_pc when a taken prediction is made.\"}, {\"file\": \"rtl/ex_stage.sv\", \"description\": \"Recompute the static prediction in EX and assert redirect only when the actual branch/jump outcome differs from the prediction.\"}], \"outcome\": \"regression\", \"fitness\": 282.82, \"delta_pct\": 0.0, \"vs_baseline\": 0.0, \"fmax_mhz\": 127.03, \"ipc_coremark\": 2e-06, \"cycles\": 4491485, \"iterations\": 10, \"lut4\": 9563, \"ff\": 1866, \"seeds\": [128.72, 127.03, 123.02], \"formal_passed\": true, \"cosim_passed\": true, \"error\": null, \"implementation_notes\": \"\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-14T01:59:16.575928Z\", \"slot\": 1, \"round_id\": 1}\n6:{\"id\": \"hyp-20260513-002-r2s1\", \"title\": \"(slot 1 hypothesis-gen failed)\", \"category\": \"structural\", \"outcome\": \"broken\", \"formal_passed\": false, \"cosim