{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778745605133,"sessionID":"ses_1da8883dfffe6GSs25zK4zURgo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"id: hyp-20260514-003-r12s2\ntitle: Add 32-entry 1-bit BHT for forward branches\ncategory: predictor\nmotivation: |\n  The current predictor handles backward loops (static taken), JAL (always taken),\n  and returns (4-entry RAS). Forward conditional branches remain unpredicted and\n  always fall through. In CoreMark's control-flow-heavy inner loops (state\n  machine, list traversal), some forward branches are biased taken; each\n  mispredict wastes a full pipeline bubble. A 32-entry 1-bit BHT adds <10 LUTs\n  and near-zero delay, offering dynamic correction for these branches without\n  touching any critical EX/MEM path.\nhypothesis: |\n  Add a 32-entry direct-mapped branch history table with 1-bit saturating\n  counters indexed by PC[6:2]. In IF, forward conditional branches consult the\n  BHT: if the bit is 1, predict taken (target is the existing b_target);\n  backward branches keep their existing static-taken override. In EX, when a\n  forward branch resolves, update the corresponding entry (set to branch_taken).\n  This should shave mispredicts on biased forward branches with negligible\n  area/Fmax cost.\nexpected_impact:\n  fitness_delta_pct: 2\n  confidence: medium\nchanges:\n  - file: rtl/bht.sv\n    description: New 32-entry 1-bit BHT module with combinational read and synchronous update.\n  - file: rtl/if_stage.sv\n    description: Add BHT read interface; use BHT output for forward branch predict_taken.\n  - file: rtl/ex_stage.sv\n    description: Add BHT update output signals (index, enable, taken) on forward branch resolution.\n  - file: rtl/core.sv\n    description: Instantiate BHT module and wire read/update ports between IF and EX stages.\n","filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep2/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r12s2.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/kimi-k2_6-rep2/cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r12s2.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260514-003-r12s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778745605126,"end":1778745605132}},"id":"prt_e257fe090001vi3T0K9P20WpER","sessionID":"ses_1da8883dfffe6GSs25zK4zURgo","messageID":"msg_e257e2ad7001Jiz9XKZAfsuyPd"}}
